Title: Knocker Nightmare
Plot: Jenna gets her cast off, but her shirt comes with it. An unwanted photo op gives everyone a chance to voice their opinion - on the most intimate of subjects. Will anyone come to her rescue and wake her up from this nightmare?
ParentalRatingReason: M Sex scenes and offensive language
GuestStars: Jessica Lu, Mike Faiola, Greer Grammer, Jesse Heiman, Catfish Jean, Anna Akana, Evan Arnold, Keith Pillow
